Description:
Icy Dock ToughArmor MB411SPO-B Drive Enclosure - Serial ATA/600 Host Interface Internal - Black - 1 x 2.5" Bay - Metal MOBILE RACK FOR ODDBAY
Introducing the ToughArmor MB411SPO-B, a full metal 2.5" SATA/SAS hard drive mobile rack designed for use in any slim ODD/FDD bay. The MB411SPO-B uses full metal construction to ensure maximum device lifespan and is capable of withstanding the harshest environments. The EZ Slide Micro tray provides hot-swap ability for hassle-free drive maintenance. Utilizing its ultra low profile design, the MB411SPO-B is a perfect storage device for system that has limited space but also requires data storage such as OEM/ODM systems, embedded control systems, factory automation systems, rackmount computers, rackmount servers and IPCs.

Almost as Slim as 2.5" Drive
The ToughArmor MB411SPO-B is designed amazingly slim and able to keep its size as small as 2.5" HDD, which makes it a complete space saver for any enterprise systems. This small form factor design allows MB411SPO-B to fit in any system that has tight space constraints such as mobile computers and embedded systems. It is also a great 2.5" mobile rack for any OEM / ODM systems that have space limitation, as system builders can easily configured their storage needs with MB411SPO-B, without wasting unnecessary space from the system.

Designed for Slim ODD & Slim FDD Bay
The MB411SPO-B is designed to fit both slim ODD and FDD bay. To use with slim FDD bay, simply unscrew three screws from metal ODD bracket and then remove the ODD bracket from the device and ready to use. With MB411SPO-B, you can quickly add a 2.5" SATA HDD / SSD to any system that has slim ODD or slim FDD bay. Or replace it with existing slim ODD / FDD device and upgrade to 2.5" solid state drive for significantly improve your overall system performance.

Removable Design with Exceptional Build Quality
The EZ Slide Micro tray supports hot-swap and makes maintenance completely hassle free in the event of a hard drive failure. With a simple swap of the hard drive, your overall down time is greatly reduced which is especially useful for time sensitive projects and applications. The tray is designed to accommodate a 7 to 9.5mm height hard drive or SSD, creating a 2.5" hot swap bay for any standard 2.5" SATA/SAS drive. Once you close the latch, the eagle-hook lock system keeps drives secured within the enclosure.
Ensuring the material used can be relied upon for many years after its deployment, the MB411SPO-B is capable of holding up in the harshest environments, with heavy duty metal construction throughout the entire device. The ToughArmor's full metal design is perfect for industrial devices that may require a flammability rating since all-metal already complies with flammability requirements. Because of the high build quality, it can be used in various enterprise systems including: military and law enforcement deployment. It can also be used in manufacturing conditions such as embedded control systems and factory automation systems.

StarTech.com Secure Charging USB Data Blocker Adapter, Male/Female USB-A Data Blocking Charge/Power-Only Charging Adapter for Phone/Tablet - USB-A data blocking charging only adapter prevents data theft/spyware/malware - Power-Only No Data Pins - Male/Female Physical Data Blocker Charger Protector - 5V/2.4A/12W max - Ideal for High Security corporate/government/defence/education/airport USB-A M/F POWER-ONLY ADAPTER
Power-Only USB-A to A Adapter
The USB-A male port of this adapter does not have physical data pins, resulting in an adapter with physical barrier for data transmission. This adapter allows you to charge your mobile devices from a laptop or desktop computer while eliminating any possibility of
Handy Adapter for Everyday Use
Portable 1.3""L x 0.7""W x 0.4""H adapter fits into your pocket or laptop bag, and lets you safely charge your smart phones, tablets, headphones, cameras, etc. in public charging stations/ports in airports, hotels and restaurants. Absence of data lines also makes this adapter safe to use in government, defense, corporate and educational environments, where connecting your mobile device may be prohibited.
Smart, Powerful and Versatile Cable
High throughput adapter delivers 5V up to 2.4A (12W max.). Smart on-board chip identifies the device's power requirements and adjusts the output accordingly. Use your existing USB-A to C, Lightning, micro-B cables to charge your appropriate devices from all USB-A power outlets - from host computers to wall chargers.
Robust and Reliable Construction
The adapter's mold is made from tough TPE plastic that offers high resilience to fraying and scratches, making it ideal for everyday rough use. Aluminium-Mylar foil shielding provides noise-free DC power to your device.
Comprehensive Product Testing & Expert Technical Support
StarTech.com conducts thorough compatibility and performance testing on all our products to ensure we are meeting or exceeding industry standards and providing high-quality products to our customers. Our local StarTech.com Technical Advisors have a broad product expertise and work directly with StarTech.com Engineers to provide support for our customers both pre and post-sales.

DESIGNED FOR G29 AND G920 DRIVING FORCE WHEELS

Lock in the right gear at the right time.
Driving Force™ Shifter is designed for both G29 and G920 Driving Force racing wheels, to enhance the latest PC and console racing titles. Add Driving Force Shifter to your racing wheel setup to complete your racing rig for a more realistic experience.
QUALITY CONSTRUCTION

Race comfortably and with confidence
With a solid steel gear shaft, Driving Force Shifter is built for precision racing and long-lasting reliability. The knob and boot are covered in high-quality, hand-stitched leather, giving it a look and feel similar to a high-performance race shifter and giving you a more comfortable, durable experience.
SIX-SPEED SHIFTER WITH PUSH-DOWN REVERSE

Maintain acceleration through every gear
The six-speed "H"-pattern shifter moves fluidly and solidly clicks into each gear, helping you execute smooth, accurate gear transitions on hairpin turns and straightaways.
SECURE MOUNTING

Won't shift while you're shifting
Durable built-in clamps allow Driving Force Shifter to be mounted securely to a table or racing rig to minimize shifting or wobbling during aggressive race maneuvers.

Description:
Plantronics Personal, Portable Bluetooth Speakerphone with 360° Audio - USB - Microphone - Battery - Portable
RICH, CLEAR AUDIO ANYWHERE
Hear and be heard, even when you're working from a remote location. The full-duplex 360° microphone makes your voice clear from up to 10 ft/3 m away. With its amplified speaker and wide frequency response, it's even great for multimedia.

BLUETOOTH CONNECTIVITY
Connect to your mobile device and tablet wirelessly-and to your PC with an integrated USB cable. Want wireless connection to your PC too? Choose the Calisto 5300 versions that come with a Bluetooth USB adapter.

Bluetooth Connectivity
Built-in Bluetooth and USB connectivity lets you connect to all your devices.
Superior Audio Quality
Enjoy full-duplex audio with 360° room coverage for easy, natural conversation.
Dynamic Mute Alert
Dynamic mute alert senses and alerts you if you talk while muted.
Compact and Portable
A soft carrying case is included for easy storage and portability.

LIKE A MOBILE CONFERENCE ROOM
You'll love how easy it is to pack up and set up-Calisto 5300 has an integrated cable management system and a convenient carrying case. And with up to 15 hours of battery life, you can host calls just about anywhere. It's practically like taking your conference room with you.

POWERING SUPERIOR MICROSOFT TEAMS EXPERIENCES
Instantly launch Microsoft Teams with a dedicated button for the quickest communications. Users benefit from the known quality experience of Poly speakerphones-the perfect communications solution for easy Microsoft Teams collaboration, conferencing and notifications.

SEAMLESS IT MANAGEMENT
Calisto 5300 is supported by Plantronics Manager Pro, a Software-as-a-Service that's sold separately. Use Plantronics Manager Pro to manage inventory, monitor usage and maintain devices. With actionable insights from Plantronics Manager Pro, IT can improve business processes, employee performance and compliance.

Description:
Logitech Cloth Gaming Mouse Pad - 11.03" x 13.39" x 0.04" Dimension - Cloth MOUSE PAD FOR GAMING MICE
Moderate surface friction
Crafted for control
Gamers using low-DPI settings, benefit from moderate resistance to the mouse feet when starting or stopping a rapid movement. Heat-treated at 200° C, the cloth surface of G240 provides just the right amount of friction for low-DPI maneuvers.

Consistent surface texture
Edge-to-edge performance
Heavy patterns and designs can interfere with sensor performance. G240 features a clean, consistent surface texture. This gives sensors better imagery for translating mouse movement into cursor movement, an improvement over inconsistent or dirty table and desk surfaces.
Matched to Logitech G sensors
Better together
Whether using an optical or laser mouse, G240 can give gamers access to enhanced sensor accuracy and precision. G240 uses a surface texture comparable to the optimal testing environment for Logitech G mice.
Stable rubber base
A winning foundation
The rubber base firmly bonded to the cloth helps keep the flexible surface in place and prevent the cloth from bunching up in front of the mouse, interfering with smooth mouse movement.
Comfortable
cloth construction
At just 1mm thick, G240 maintains a low profile. The soft fabric improves comfort as the wrist moves back and forth across the mouse pad's edge.
Roll for transport
Take it with you
With a flexible cloth construction, G240 rolls up for easy transport and lies flat when you're ready to play. Protect the mouse pad when you take it to LAN events using the hexagonal packaging.
